<DOCNO> LA041094-0045 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 030811 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 10, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Book Review; Page 15; Book Review Desk 
</P>
