134 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
JUST THE FACTS; CRUISE SHIP SCORES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Cruise ship sanitation scores for some of the ships inspected in January and 
