<P>
 How in God's name can your reporters keep from laughing in the faces of the 
police spokesman? Do the police actually believe the public is that stupid? 
Their silence, followed by obscene explanations, is beyond belief. 
</P>
<P>
 PHILIP CURTIS 
</P>
