<DOCID> 030903 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 10, 1994, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 13; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
891 words 
