<DOCNO> LA041094-0142 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 030908 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 10, 1994, Sunday, Bulldog Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 1; Column 1; Sports Desk 
