COMMUNITY NEWS: CENTRAL: CHINATOWN; 2 JOURNALISTS TO BE HONORED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Two Chinese American television journalists will be honored by the Chinese 
Historical Society of Southern California at its annual spring banquet 
fund-raiser April 23 at the new Ming's Pavilion Restaurant, 911 N. Broadway. 
</P>
<P>
 Frank Kwan, a longtime producer at KNBC-TV Channel 4, and Sam Chu Lin, an 
