<P>
 VERNON 
</P>
<P>
 (3 seats) * There are no challengers to the reelection of three incumbents, so 
the city canceled its election. 
</P>
<P>
 * denotes incumbent On the Cover 
</P>
<P>
 South Gate City Council candidates wait for their turns at the podium as 
another gives a speech during a recent forum. 
</P>
<P>
 Council elections, and politics in general, in the Southeast Los Angeles 
County Hub Cities are often characterized by finger-pointing, name-calling and 
sometimes bizarre accusations. Experts say the political instability in those 
cities is a reflection of demographic and economic upheaval. 
</P>
<P>
 The messy incidents so common to Southeast politics are "blemishes of 
perfectibility on the road to democracy," said H. Eric Schockman, a writer and 
professor of California municipal politics at USC. 
</P>
